https://github.com/slowtorta/turtlewow-bug-tracker/assets/35845488/182a637f-08dc-4cb4-85ae-5ccfedd681a3

As you can see in this video, I made the server print all packets it receives, and there is nothing received at all when i click the "Join as Group" button. The issue needs to be assigned to a client interface developer.
